Regulation (EC) No 1899/97 is amended as follows:
1. in Article 1, the first paragraph is replaced by the following: "All imports into the Community under the arrangements provided for by Regulations (EC) No 2290/2000, (EC) No 2433/2000, (EC) No 2434/2000, (EC) No 2435/2000 and (EC) No 2851/2000 of products covered by Annex I to this Regulation shall be subject to presentation of an import licence.";
2. part A of Annex I is deleted.
